My current night skincare routine 🌙

COSRX Vitamin C 13 
- This serum contains super vitamin E and hyaluronic acid. It improves skin condition and even out skin tone. It’s fast-absorbent and feels lightweight on the skin. It has also reduced my dark spots around my chin. 

COSRX Ultimate Nourishing Rice Overnight Spa Mask
- It was my first time to try an overnight mask and I was so excited to apply and see how my skin would feel like the next morning. It’s easy to rinse and I instantly felt how it made my skin softer. I also love that it’s non-sticky and a little goes a long way.

COSRX Lip Sleep Propolis Lip Sleeping Mask
- I truly appreciate this lip mask for having a small scooper for easier application and hygiene purposes. It’s definitely one of the most moisturizing lip products that I’ve tried. Since I apply this at night, I no longer wake up with dry lips.

COSRX Acne Pimple Master Patch
- The pimple patch I use is really from COSRX and this one arrived just in time since I only have one patch left from my previous pack. It was very effective and has remained the same until now. This is even nicer because it comes with different sizes and still is transparent which can be used under makeup.
